That's how it always ends
if the man's not Carter.

14
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:35,760
Time Master Druce?

15
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:37,160
You and your band
of rogues have run rampant

16
00:00:37,240 --> 00:00:38,240
throughout history.

17
00:00:38,320 --> 00:00:39,680
This is why we work alone.

18
00:00:39,760 --> 00:00:41,040
