19
00:00:41,120 --> 00:00:43,640
The Time Masters have issued
Omega Protocols on all of us.

20
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:45,320
- They've sent the Pilgrim.
- Who's the Pilgrim?

21
00:00:45,400 --> 00:00:48,000
The Pilgrim is the Time Masters'
most deadly assassin.

22
00:00:48,080 --> 00:00:50,080
She's hunting our younger selves.

23
00:00:51,400 --> 00:00:55,040
Kaylex Druzan,
you have been found guilty

24
00:00:55,120 --> 00:00:57,080
of time piracy in the first degree...

25
00:00:58,360 --> 00:01:01,240
{\an5}and sentenced to death
via Omega Protocol.

26
00:01:02,680 --> 00:01:05,520
The Pilgrim has made contact
with your younger self.

27
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:10,760
This will all be over quickly.

28
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:25,080
Well done.
Here's your next assignment.

29
00:01:26,080 --> 00:01:28,920
These individuals
have manipulated the timeline

30
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:31,680
