on multiple occasions.

31
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:36,240
You are hereby ordered to hunt down
these individuals' younger selves

32
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:37,880
and eliminate them.

33
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:47,360
This isn't my element.

34
00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:50,000
- It's mine.
- Just keep a weather eye open

35
00:01:50,080 --> 00:01:51,080
for the Pilgrim.

36
00:01:51,160 --> 00:01:52,920
Gideon calculates a 97 percent chance

37
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,240
that she will attack
your younger self

38
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:56,200
in this exact time and place.

39
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,280
Roll it.

40
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:04,160
Young Rory's not in there.

41
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:07,240
But we found his parents.
They're dead.

42
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:08,440
Then where the hell is he?

43
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:25,720
Come with me if you want to live.

44
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,040
I always wanted to say that.

45
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,720
{\an5}- That's younger you?
- What'd you tell him?

46
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,840
{\an5}That we work for a secret
agency called A.R.G.U.S.

47
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:43,760
- I think he bought it.
- Course he did.

48
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:44,840
He's an idiot.

49
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:48,480
{\an5}Hey, no offense, but do you
really think it's a good idea

50
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,840
{\an5}to leave him unsupervised?

51
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:53,720
You're right. Have fun.

52
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,840
You seem calm.

53
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:56,840
You mean considering
a temporal bounty hunter

54
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:58,640
is trying to murder
our younger selves?

55
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:01,840
{\an5}I was gonna put it a little more
delicately than that, but yeah.

56
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:05,120
{\an5}I think at some point, you just learn
to live with a sword over your head.

57
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:12,400
{\an5}Either you're getting better
or I'm getting lazy.

58
00:03:14,040 --> 00:03:16,120
So it seems like you decided
to ignore the advice

59
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:18,200
from Old West you
about not being with Ray.

60
