was your advice, remember?

61
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:22,080
{\an5}Don't listen to my advice.

62
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:26,240
{\an5}- So did you tell him what she said?
- Oh, sure.

63
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:29,360
{\an5}"Hey, Ray, by the way,
