before I have to drop

68
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,920
the whole doomed love affair thing
on his head.

69
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:41,600
{\an5}Yeah, I mean, who wants
a relationship based on honesty

70
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,760
{\an5}and communication?

71
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,360
{\an5}Believe me.

72
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:46,280
A relationship based
on an ancient Egyptian curse

73
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,440
doesn't work much better.

74
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,080
Mr. Rory, how are you feeling?

75
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,400
{\an5}I mean, your younger self.

76
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,640
{\an5}Jax is watching him.

77
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:56,680
{\an5}That young man,
you, just lost his family.

78
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:58,280
You might want a shoulder to cry on.

79
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:00,000
{\an5}I don't cry, Professor.

80
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:02,320
{\an5}Oh, and Haircut,
thanks for saving me.

81
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,400
You're welcome.

82
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,880
{\an5}You know what I don't get
is why doesn't the Pilgrim

83
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:07,040
{\an5}just go back a week earlier
and kill younger Rory then?

84
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:09,080
{\an5}'Cause the Omega Protocol
calls for precision.

85
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:12,080
{\an5}Multiple attempts from the Pilgrim
could do irreparable temporal damage.

86
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:14,840
{\an5}Which means she's only got one shot
at killing each and every one of us.

87
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:17,400
{\an5}And we only have one shot
to extract your younger selves

88
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:19,720
{\an5}from the timeline
before she pulls the trigger.

89
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:22,960
{\an5}<i>Sir, based on the temporal wake
generated by the Pilgrim's time ship,</i>

90
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,800
{\an5}<i>I calculate a 96 percent likelihood</i>

91
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:27,640
{\an5}<i>that she is heading
