00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:37,120
- Name?
- Lance.

94
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,240
Sara Lance.

95
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:39,880
This is ridiculous.

96
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:42,840
{\an5}Come on. I thought it was
Take Your Daughter to Work Day.

97
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,840
{\an5}Yeah, if I was in grade school.

98
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,560
{\an5}"Daddy, I'm doing a paper
on the criminal justice system.

99
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:48,080
