108
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:29,600
Get out of here. Get out of here!
Go, go, go!

109
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:09,400
- God, she's...
- Quite the badass.

110
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,640
{\an5}I put her in the cargo bay
with mini you,

111
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,920
