at any time,

132
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:11,000
she could be killing any of us
right now.

133
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:13,640
- And if we die in the past...
- We die in the present.

134
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:15,360
Wow. So interesting.

135
00:07:15,440 --> 00:07:17,000
How long does it take
for what happens in the past

136
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:19,000
to affect the present?

137
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:20,720
Could I be dead right now
and not know it?

138
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,920
Maybe I am dead right now.

139
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:25,760
- Hello? Can anybody hear me?
- No.

140
00:07:25,840 --> 00:07:27,240
Look, the important thing
is not to panic.

141
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:29,600
Somebody's playing Russian roulette
with our younger selves.

142
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,680
Why would we panic?

143
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:31,960
Well, there are a few exceptions.

144
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,640
Kendra's ability to reincarnate

145
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:36,720
