told us about your past, Rip.

151
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:53,440
And I don't trust a man with secrets.

152
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:56,160
Look, the less information
you have to offer on me,

153
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:59,640
the less valuable you are
to our now numerous enemies.

154
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:02,080
Like I said, convenient.

155
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:04,040
- Are they fighting?
- This is not a fight.

156
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,880
