167
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,000
No.

168
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:31,120
Hey, when do I get to go home?

169
00:08:31,200 --> 00:08:33,360
You're safer here. Trust me.

170
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,680
Well, where is here?

171
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:36,120
