172
00:08:36,920 --> 00:08:38,880
Please, will you just tell me
what the hell's going on?

173
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:41,320
Look, it's safer for you if I don't.

174
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:42,800
And we look alike, because...

175
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:46,000
because we're like family.

176
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,400
And I need you to trust me.

177
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:50,920
Look, my dad,
he's got to be freaking out.

178
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,000
If he ever lost me...

179
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,080
